{"tid":1306672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔廣福邨女子墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-07-11T08:44:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T08:47:39.000Z","uid":13663,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"302dc67ecc9ea518d2ea85a06268f6d7b27a9ac3","tid":1306672,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:44:18.000Z","msg":"大埔廣福邨女子墮樓亡，今午（11日）2時28分，一名女子被發現於廣仁樓高處墮下，跌落一樓簷篷，發出一聲巨響。女事主重創昏迷，救援人員接報趕至，將她救下，並送往大埔那打素醫院搶救，惟送院後證實傷重不治，警方正調查事主身份及墮樓原因。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f643588e992e30754dc116c7e97948c3c1376369","tid":1306672,"uid":44028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:45:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94194304f0ea0629212d884878a11c5cd184f18c","tid":1306672,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:46:17.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"8f77cba1b1ac23c73fc6840d4fbbeae594b624ca","tid":1306672,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T08:47:39.000Z","msg":"rip"}]}